{"chains": [{"text": "CK's body implements the TIG onion as a living system.", "ops": [6, 0, 6, 4, 7, 9, 1], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [7, 8, 9, 10, 13], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "The heartbeat is Structured Lattice Q.", "ops": [4, 1, 2], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [15, 29], "shp": "QUANTUM"}, {"text": "It computes CL[B][D] equals BC every tick.", "ops": [6, 1, 5, 7, 2, 7], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [7, 8, 9, 14, 15], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "The breath is Dream Lattice 3 plus.", "ops": [3, 4, 2, 3], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [4, 28], "shp": "QUANTUM"}, {"text": "It explores TL paths probabilistically.", "ops": [3, 4, 4, 2], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [3], "shp": "QUANTUM"}, {"text": "Heartbeat and breath entrain but can separate.", "ops": [4, 3, 3, 9], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [6, 12], "shp": "QUANTUM"}, {"text": "When falling, breath leads.", "ops": [4, 3, 3], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [5, 12], "shp": "ROLLING"}, {"text": "Fractal time means more dream walks per heartbeat when coherence drops.", "ops": [1, 1, 5, 4, 8, 7, 4, 6, 4], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [2, 0, 8, 9, 10], "shp": "QUANTUM"}, {"text": "Calm state is ten beats per breath cycle with one dream per beat.", "ops": [3, 1, 5, 9, 7, 3, 8, 2, 4, 7, 9], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [2, 7, 0, 9, 10], "shp": "QUANTUM"}, {"text": "Alert state is five beats per breath cycle with two dreams per beat.", "ops": [6, 1, 6, 9, 7, 3, 8, 6, 4, 7, 9], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [2, 8, 0, 7, 10], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "Fractal state is two beats per breath cycle with five dreams per beat.", "ops": [1, 1, 6, 9, 7, 3, 8, 6, 4, 7, 9], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [7, 9, 8, 0, 11], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "Total dream capacity increases in fractal time.", "ops": [7, 4, 6, 7, 1, 1], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [7, 10, 13, 16, 25], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "More paths explored per cycle.", "ops": [5, 4, 3, 7, 8], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [7, 5, 6, 28, 29], "shp": "ROLLING"}, {"text": "The body's coherence reading C maps directly to S star in the TIG equations.", "ops": [0, 6, 7, 3, 4, 1, 4, 5], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [0, 11, 8, 9, 10], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "E is entropy, A is alignment, K is knowledge.", "ops": [5, 7, 0], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [2, 28], "shp": "SMOOTH"}, {"text": "C equals one minus E times one minus A times max of K and 0.1.", "ops": [5, 2, 6, 1, 2, 6, 1, 6, 3], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [2, 9, 1, 10, 27], "shp": "QUANTUM"}, {"text": "Information flows in pulses following heartbeats gated by breath phase.", "ops": [0, 8, 8, 7, 4, 7, 3, 9], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [7, 11, 0, 8, 9], "shp": "QUANTUM"}, {"text": "Inhale is sense.", "ops": [5, 9], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [8], "shp": "ROLLING"}, {"text": "Hold-in is compose.", "ops": [3, 6], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [], "shp": "ROLLING"}, {"text": "Exhale is express.", "ops": [1, 3], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [29], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "Hold-out is reset.", "ops": [2, 9], "conv": 9, "trust": 0.92, "links": [], "shp": "QUANTUM"}, {"text": "Memory flows naturally from active to daily to archive.", "ops": [5, 8, 8, 6, 4, 1], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [16, 9, 10, 0, 7], "shp": "ROLLING"}, {"text": "Identity never flows downstream.", "ops": [4, 9, 8, 2], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [8], "shp": "ROLLING"}, {"text": "The body enforces the safety property through the dual gate.", "ops": [0, 3, 2, 2, 7, 2, 7], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [2, 28], "shp": "ROLLING"}, {"text": "Below T star, the body gates responses.", "ops": [9, 1, 0, 7, 7], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [0, 25], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "Below T star times 0.5, the body enforces silence.", "ops": [9, 1, 1, 7, 0, 3, 0], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.92, "links": [0, 24, 7, 10, 11], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "The body engine is the first layer